Extract out and use common functoin `__Pyx_PyMethodDescr_Check `

comment_data.body: These deserve their own utility code section, so that other parts of Cython can use the functions directly.
Not sure why we're keeping this (since it's unused here and not as good as the full version I think)
Right, it's unused. Just remove it.
I am a little bit confused about whether this should remain in the code or not
This would be an error case, not just false/0.
